apps.name: iPogo
apps.localizedDescription:
iPogo is the worlds best iOS PokemonGo Joystick and Spoofing toolset 

Features:
-Teleport/Snipe
-Feeds (Pokémon/Quest/Raids)
-Map & S2 Overlay (L14/17 cells)
-Nearby Pokémon Overlay
-Favorites (Routes/Hotspots/Coords)
-Stats Inventory
-Joystick Overlay
-Enhanced Throw
-Autowalk
-Encounter IV
-Nearby Gym Slot Scanner
-Jailbreak Tweak
-Journal
-Tap To Walk
-60 fps

apps.name: Instagram Rocket
apps.versionDescription: First featured version of Instagram Rocket
apps.localizedDescription:
Adds new features to Instagram

-Save any photo or video to Camera Roll
-Hold down on an image or video to view high resolution version of it
-Double tap or hold on a profile picture to view it in full-screen
-Mute and unmute users from home and activity feed
-Hide sponsored ads
-Show following status on user profile
-Share images with third-party apps
-View direct messages without notifying sender
-Change feed layout between grid or list view
-Shows confirmation message when double tapping a post to like it
-View exact timestamp of a post (date and time)|n-View stories without marking them as seen
-Download photos and videos from stories
-Manually mark stories as seen
-Show entire gallery instead of last 24 hours in story maker
